<Section xmlns="urn:com.io7m.structural:8:0"
         xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
         title="generate-keypair">

  <Subsection title="Name">
    <Paragraph>
      <Term type="command">generate-keypair</Term> - Generate keypairs
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <Term type="command">generate-keypair</Term> command generates keypairs.
    </Paragraph>

    <FormalItem title="Parameters">
      <xi:include href="CSGenerateKeyPair.xml"/>
    </FormalItem>

    <Paragraph>
      The <Term type="command">generate-keypair</Term> command will generate a keypair and write the private key
      to the file specified with <Term type="parameter">--private-key</Term>, and write the public key to the file
      specified with <Term type="parameter">--public-key</Term>. If the key files already exist, they will not be
      overwritten unless the <Term type="parameter">--overwrite</Term> parameter is specified.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      If the command encounters no errors or warnings, it will not print anything.
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

